 F(x) = \int_a^x f(y) \, dy, \quad G(x) = \int_a^x g(y) \, dy ,
 \int_a^b F(x) g(x) \, dx + \int_a^b f(x) G(x) \, dx 
 = \int_{x=a}^b \int_{y=a}^x f(y) g(x) \, dy \, dx + \int_{x=a}^b \int_{y=a}^x f(x) g(y) \, dy \, dx 
